modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8823:"<p>Vit Nam c tc  pht trin Internet ng th 8 ti Chu  v th 20 trn th gii. Tuy nhin, cc chuyn gia v pht trin Web trn th gii nh gi cc website xut pht t Vit Nam l cc sn phm ca thi k  . Nm bt c iu , izwebz  ng ra ng ti tr v t chc hi tho mang tn WDC cng vi cc nh ti tr khc nh: Mediart Academy, QHOnline, VietDesigner, Y2graphic,&#8230;<br />\n<span id="more-5572"></span></p>\n<h5>WDC l g?</h5>\n<p>WDC c vit tt bi cm t Web Development Conference &#8211; Hi tho pht trin web. y l chng trnh hi tho thng nin c t chc mi nm hai ln ti thnh ph H Ch Minh v H Ni, hi tho thng c t chc vo trung tun ca thng 4 v thng 9. WDC c t chc vi quy m ln v tp trung nhiu din gi c kinh nghim cng nh cc ch  u mang tnh cht thi i.</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image"><a href="http://wdc.org.vn" title="WDC 2013" target="_blank"><img src="http://wdc.org.vn/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/3070j.gif" alt="WDC 2013" /></a></div>\n<h5>V sao cn hi tho WDC?</h5>\n<p> hn 15 nm k t khi Internet t nn mng ti Vit Nam. Website  dn dn tr thnh mt phn rt quan trng i vi c nhn/doanh nghip v c hng trm l do  th hin tm quan trng . Ngy nay, vi s bng n ca internet bng thng rng, cc dch v thit k website  t ra i  c th p ng c nhu cu ca cc c nhn v doanh nghip. Vic xy dng mt website hon ton khng kh, nhng  c c mt website tht s cht lng th ta nh tm kim y bin. Thm vo , phn ln cc website ti Vit Nam ch yu ch l s sao chp, lp li my mc v km phn sng to. Chnh v th, m cc chuyn gia v pht trin Web trn th gii nh gi cc website xut pht t Vit Nam l cc sn phm ca thi k  .</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image"><a href="http://wdc.org.vn" title="WDC 2013" target="_blank"><img src="http://wdc.org.vn/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/800x1000-015.jpg" alt="WDC Poster" /></a></div>\n<h5>Hi tho din ra nguyn ngy 15/09/2013</h5>\n<p>WDC 2013 din ra t 07:30 AM n 17:30 PM ngy 15/09/2013. Bui sng chng ta s nghe cc speaker ni nhiu v Branding, Web Desgin, HTML5 &#8211; CSS3, Responsive Web Design,&#8230; Bui chiu s c cc chuyn gia trong lnh vc Web Developer tr chuyn, thuyt ging v cc ngn ng lp trnh v cc framework ph bin, gip cho i tng tham d s c c mt ci nhn ng v hng i ph hp trn con ng mnh  la chn. Chng trnh chi tit bn hy xem qua ti y nh:<a href=" http://wdc.org.vn/chuong-trinh/" title=" http://wdc.org.vn/chuong-trinh/" target="_blank"> http://wdc.org.vn/chuong-trinh/</a></p>\n<h5>V sao bn phi tham gia WDC 2013</h5>\n<p><strong>1/ Din gi:</strong> im c bit chnh l WDC2013  mi nhng din gi c nhiu kinh nghim trong thit k v lp trnh web. H s chia s tt c nhng g h bit,  bn c th nh hng c tng lai, cng nh xc nh c bc i tip theo trn hnh trnh cng ngh m mnh la chn.</p>\n<p><strong>2/ Ni dung:</strong> WDC2013 vi ch  chnh l &#8220;I Build Website&#8221; s bao gm cc topic chuyn su cc cng ngh lp trnh v thit k web (HTML5&#038;CSS3, Responsive design, Framework,&#8230;). Ngoi ra cn cc topic v pht trin v qun l website hiu qu.</p>\n<p><strong>3/ Tri nghim:</strong> n vi WDC2013 bn s c ha mnh vo cng ng, c cng cc din gi v tho lun v cc im nng trong tnh hnh website ti Vit Nam, cng nh trao i v phng hng, ng li pht trin trong tng lai.</p>\n<p><strong>4/ C hi:</strong> y l c hi mt nm ch c mt ln  cc Web designer, Web developer cng t hp li v cng nhau chia s nhng tht bi, kinh nghim  i n thnh cng. Ngoi ra, khi tham d bn s nhn c nhng phn qu c gi tr ln n t cc nh ti tr ca WDC.<br />\nThng tin chi tit cc bn c th xem qua ti website <a href="http://wdc.org.vn" title="http://wdc.org.vn" target="_blank">http://wdc.org.vn</a></p>\n<h5>i tng tham d</h5>\n<p>Mi ngi u c th tham gia. Hc sinh, sinh vin, ngi sp bc vo ging ng i hc, ngi ang phn vn v ngh nghip, nhng ngi trong ngnh, nhng k ngoi o, tt c u c th gp phn lm nn s thnh cng dnh cho WDC 2013.<br />\nHy cng chung tay pht biu v to nn s thn mt cho hi tho WDC 2013 nh.</p>\n<h5>Hi tho + Buffet ch 200.000 </h5>\n<p>Hi tho din ra nguyn ngy, nu  cc bn t do n ung s rt mt thi gian. Do , BTC quyt nh s t chc tic buffet tra bn ngoi snh ca phng hi tho?  chng ta c th va n buffet tra, va tr chuyn vi cc din gi.</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image"><img src="http://wdc.org.vn/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/900X200-05-01.png" alt="Buffet 200k" /></div>\n<p>Vy n vi WDC 2013 vi chi ph 200.000  c mc qu khng? HON TON KHNG. Nu bn tnh k, gi v buffet hin ti cng > 150.000  ri. Ngoi ra, WDC cn c tea-break gia cc bui sng v chiu, cc bn s c thng thc tr, cafe, nc ngt, beer, bnh ngt v tri cy,&#8230;. Vy va i hi tho, va c n ung tri nghim, m gi ch 200.000  th qu re ri cn g na?<br />\nn vi WDC 2013 ti Tp.HCM bn hon ton c th t mnh tri nghim nhng g mi nht, tuyt vi nht trong th gii Web v tn. Bn c th cng cc din gi trao i thng tin, hc hi ln nhau, cng nhau n ung v suy ngh. Khi n vi WDC bn s c c hi nhn c cc hc bng/qu tng cc hp dn v gi tr t cc nh ti tr chnh ca WDC nh Mediart Academy, QHOnline, Izwebz,&#8230;..</p>\n<h5>C hi hp dn</h5>\n<p>Vo ngy 16/08/2013 WDC  cng b 5 bn u tin ginh c qu tng t izwebz.com. Cng vi khi th , BTC WDC  tin hnh t chc thm chng trnh &#8220;<a href="http://wdc.org.vn/con-so-may-man-dot-ii/" target="_blank">Con s may mn II</a>&#8221; dnh cho cc bn cha mn mn  t trc v cc  ng k t v trc ngy 30/08/2013. Vi nhng gii thng hp dn hn c ln u tin, o c logo izwebz, wdc, ly wdc v coupon gim gi t <a href="http://qhonline.info" target="_blank">qhonline.info</a>. Thng tin chi tit cc bn c th xem qua <a href="http://wdc.org.vn/con-so-may-man-dot-ii/" target="_blank">ti y</a>.</p>\n<h5>ng k tham gia?</h5>\n<div class="tutorial-image"><a href="http://wdc.org.vn/dat-mua-ve/" title="Mua v" target="_blank"><img src="http://wdc.org.vn/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/90x200-03.png" alt="" /></a></div>\n<p>Cc bn c th ng k tham gia hi tho ti website chnh thc ca WDC: <a href="http://wdc.org.vn/dat-mua-ve/" title="WDC Vit Nam" target="_blank">http://wdc.org.vn</a>. Mi thc mc cc bn c th gi mail v hello[at]wdc.org.vn hoc tham gia vo <a href="https://www.facebook.com/hello.wdc" title="WDC in Facebook" target="_blank">facebook page ca WDC 2013</a>  cp nht c cc thng tin mi nht v hi tho.</p>\n<p>Hy ng k ngay thi, cn chn ch g na ch? C hi khng dnh cho ngi hay do d.</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image-small">\n<div class="fb-like-box" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/hello.wdc" data-width="292" data-show-faces="true" data-header="false" data-stream="false" data-show-border="false"></div>\n</div>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:79:"http://www.izwebz.com/uncategorized/moi-tham-du-hoi-thao-wdc-2013-tai-hcm/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2:"22";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:34:"PSD sang HTML  BUSSINESS LAYOUT";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:57:"http://www.izwebz.com/css/psd-sang-html-bussiness-layout/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:66:"http://www.izwebz.com/css/psd-sang-html-bussiness-layout/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 06 Aug 2013 10:35:51 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3:"CSS";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:29:"http://www.izwebz.com/?p=5529";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:597:"Xin cho tt c cc bn. Mnh l Tommy, l ngi mi ca izwebz. y l bi tutorial u tin ca mnh. Trong bi tut ny th mnh s hng dn bn convert mt giao din website doanh nghip t PSD sang HTML. Tuy trn izwebz  c vi tut v PSD sang HTML nhng mnh ngh y l bc quan trng trong thit k website nn nu lm thm vi tutorial na chc cng khng sao. y l giao din chng ta s lm trong ln ny : Bn download phn source code v, trong  folder images  [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5:"Tommy";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:35405:"<p>Xin cho tt c cc bn. Mnh l Tommy, l ngi mi ca izwebz. y l bi tutorial u tin ca mnh.</p>\n<p>Trong bi tut ny th mnh s hng dn bn convert mt giao din website doanh nghip t PSD sang HTML. Tuy trn izwebz  c vi tut v PSD sang HTML nhng mnh ngh y l bc quan trng trong thit k website nn nu lm thm vi tutorial na chc cng khng sao.<br />\n<span id="more-5529"></span></p>\n<p>y l giao din chng ta s lm trong ln ny :</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image">\n    <img src="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/tommy/tutorial/images/demo.jpg" alt="demo_series3" />\n</div>\n<p>Bn download phn source code v, trong  folder images  c file psd  bn xem thm. Ton b cc hnh cn thit mnh  slice ht ri.</p>\n<p>Phn u tin, ta s xy dng code HTML :</p>\n<h5>Bc 1 :</h5>\n<p>u tin, chng ta vit cc th div trc  nh ra cu trc trang, cc bn hy xem hnh sau  hnh dung ra cu trc ca trang web :</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image">\n    <img src="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/tommy/tutorial/images/cautruc.jpg" alt="cautruc" />\n</div>\n<p>Theo hnh trn, code ca chng ta nh sau :</p>\n<pre class="brush: xml; title: ; notranslate">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN&quot;\r\n&quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;html xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot; xml:lang=&quot;en&quot; lang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Business&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;Content-Type&quot; content=&quot;text/html; charset=utf-8&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; type=&quot;text/css&quot; href=&quot;style.css&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=&quot;wrapper&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;div id=&quot;top_page&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!--end #top_page--&gt;\r\n		\r\n		&lt;div id=&quot;header&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;div id=&quot;banner&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!--end #banner--&gt;\r\n			&lt;div id=&quot;featured_post&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!--end #featured_post--&gt;\r\n		&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!--end #header--&gt;	\r\n		\r\n		&lt;div id=&quot;content&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!--end #content--&gt;\r\n		\r\n		&lt;div id=&quot;footer&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!--end #footer--&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!--end #wrapper--&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n\r\n</pre>\n<h5>Bc 2 : TOP PAGE</h5>\n<p>Theo nh hnh trn, cc bn thy phn top page bao gm logo ca trang, phn phone number v cc pages ca trang web. i vi logo, chng ta dng th img ; i vi pages, ta dng ul ; cn i vi phone, cc bn thy n c background l hnh ci phone, do  chng ta dng th a (sau ny lm link n trang contact)  t background, cn ci background xm xm  ngoi th cn phi dng mt block element bao ngoi ci tag a  set width v height,  y mnh dng p (v p l 1 block element). Code ca chng ta nh sau (phn code ny bn t trong div#top_page):</p>\n<pre class="brush: xml; title: ; notranslate">\r\n&lt;img src=&quot;images/logo.png&quot; alt=&quot;logo&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;p id=&quot;telephone&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;123-456-7890&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul id=&quot;pages&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;bold uppercase&quot;&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;bold uppercase&quot;&gt;About&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;bold uppercase&quot;&gt;Services&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;bold uppercase&quot;&gt;Portfolio&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;bold uppercase&quot;&gt;Contact&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n</pre>\n<p>Trong code HTML ca giao din ny ti c t class bold v uppercase vo mt s tags (nh cc bn thy trong phn code trn),  sau ny chng ta style trong CSS class bold c font-weight l bold v class uppercase text-transform l uppercase.</p>\n<p>n y, chng ta c giao din nh <a href="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/tommy/tutorial/demo%20post%201%20%28html%29/top_page.html" title="top page" target="_blank">demo</a>.</p>\n<h5>Bc 3 : HEADER</h5>\n<p>Bn trong div#header ny s gm 2 div nh :</p>\n<h5>a) BANNER</h5>\n<p>i vi cu &#8220;We have what it takes to take your website to the new height of success&#8221; th ta dng tag p vi id l success. i vi cu &#8220;Get started here&#8221; th dng tag p vi id l started, ngoi ra trong p#started ny mnh cn thm mt tag span na nhm  t background l ci hnh mi tn. Cui cng l mt tag img   a hnh banner vo. Phn code ny bn t trong div#banner :</p>\n<pre class="brush: xml; title: ; notranslate">\r\n&lt;p id=&quot;success&quot;&gt;\r\nWe have what it takes to take your website to the &lt;span class=&quot;uppercase bold&quot;&gt;new height of success&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			\r\n&lt;p id=&quot;started&quot; class=&quot;uppercase bold&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Get started here&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;img src=&quot;images/banner.png&quot; alt=&quot;banner&quot; /&gt;\r\n\r\n</pre>\n<h5>b) Phn FEATURED POST</h5>\n<p>Ta s dng tag ul, mi bi featured post l mt tag li. Mc d tag ul  l block element, nhng mnh phi dng thm th div  bao quanh ul ny  khi style CSS, mnh t padding cho ul th khng nh hng n  ln ca th div bn ngoi (bn nn xem li bi <a href="http://www.izwebz.com/css/do-lon-thuc-su-cua-box/"> ln tht s ca box</a> ca anh Demon Warlock  hiu r vn  ny). Trong mi li, chng ta cn mt img v p. Bn t phn code sau trong div#featured_post :</p>\n<pre class="brush: xml; title: ; notranslate">\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		&lt;img src=&quot;images/post-icon1.png&quot; alt=&quot;post icon&quot; /&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Save big with us&lt;/span&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		&lt;img src=&quot;images/post-icon2.png&quot; alt=&quot;post icon&quot; /&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Always on time&lt;/span&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		&lt;img src=&quot;images/post-icon3.png&quot; alt=&quot;post icon&quot; /&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Contact Us&lt;/span&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n</pre>\n<p>Bn c th xem <a href="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/tommy/tutorial/demo%20post%201%20%28html%29/header.html" title="header_html" target="_blank">demo</a>.</p>\n<h5>Bc 4 : CONTENT</h5>\n<p>Cc post item c style ging nhau nn i vi mi post th chng ta dng mt tag div c class l post_item. Phn tiu  th mnh dng th h1 lng thm th a link ti post .<br />\nMt img l tm hnh ca mi post. Mt th p l on paragraph, cui cng l th a vi class l read_more. Ring i vi bi post  gia th n ko c th a read more v c mt unorder list. Trong div#content, code ca chng ta nh sau :</p>\n<pre class="brush: xml; title: ; notranslate">\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;post_item&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Who we are ?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;img src=&quot;images/post-image1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;post image&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Etiam tristique tristique lacus in varius. Donec nec vestibulum ligula. Aenean turpis diam, feugiat a luctus in, rhoncus eget risus. Maecenas consequat porttitor dui, vitae consequat massa imperdiet ut. elit ut tempus lobortis, eros leo molestie velit, non egestas augue nulla eget erat.\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;uppercase bold read_more&quot;&gt;Read more&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!--end .post_item--&gt;\r\n	\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;post_item&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;What we do ?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;img src=&quot;images/post-image2.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;post image&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n	Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Etiam tristique tristique lacus in varius. Donec nec vestibulum ligula. Aenean turpis diam, feugiat a luctus in, rhoncus eget risus. Maecenas consequat porttitor dui, vitae consequat massa imperdiet ut. elit ut tempus lobortis, eros leo molestie velit, non egestas augue nulla eget erat.\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		\r\n	&lt;ul&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Website Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Blog Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Branding design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!--end .post_item--&gt;\r\n	\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;post_item&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;h1&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Why hire us ?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n	&lt;img src=&quot;images/post-image3.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;post image&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Etiam tristique tristique lacus in varius. Donec nec vestibulum ligula. Aenean turpis diam, feugiat a luctus in, rhoncus eget risus. Maecenas consequat porttitor dui, vitae consequat massa imperdiet ut. elit ut tempus lobortis, eros leo molestie velit, non egestas augue nulla eget erat.\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;uppercase bold read_more&quot;&gt;Read more&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!--end .post_item--&gt;\r\n</pre>\n<p>Xong phn code trn, bn xem <a href="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/tommy/tutorial/demo%20post%201%20%28html%29/content.html" title="content_html" target="_blank">demo</a>.</p>\n<h5>Bc 5 : FOOTER</h5>\n<p>i vi phn cui cng ny, chng ta cn 2 tag ul. Tag ul th nht c id l info_footer nu mt vi thng tin thm, tag ul th 2 c id l copy_power ghi copyright v power bi WordPress. Trong div#footer, chng ta vit nt phn code cui cng :</p>\n<pre class="brush: xml; title: ; notranslate">\r\n&lt;ul id=&quot;info_footer&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		&lt;h3&gt;Browse Site&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n		&lt;ul&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;About our company&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Contact us&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Our Portfolio&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Our Prices&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Online quote form&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Client Testimonials&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		&lt;h3&gt;Our Testimonials&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n		Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Etiam tristique tristique lacus in varius. Donec nec vestibulum ligula. Aenean turpis diam, feugiat a luctus in, rhoncus eget risus. Maecenas consequat porttitor dui, vitae consequat massa imperdiet ut. elit ut tempus lobortis, eros leo molestie velit. &lt;span class=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Rafi, GraphicsFuel.com&lt;/span&gt;\r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		\r\n	&lt;li&gt;\r\n		&lt;h3&gt;From Our Blog&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			&lt;span class=&quot;date&quot;&gt;July 6, 2013&lt;/span&gt;\r\n			&lt;span class=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur&lt;/span&gt; adipiscing elit. Etiam tristique tristique lacus in varius. Donec nec vestibulum ligula. Aenean turpis diam...\r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			&lt;span class=&quot;date&quot;&gt;July 6, 2013&lt;/span&gt;\r\n			&lt;span class=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur&lt;/span&gt; adipiscing elit. Etiam tristique tristique lacus in varius. Donec nec vestibulum ligula. Aenean turpis diam...\r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;!--end #info--&gt;\r\n	\r\n&lt;ul id=&quot;copy_power&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Copyright &amp;copy; 2013 Business. All rights reserved. Designed by izwebz.com&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li class=&quot;uppercase bold&quot;&gt;Power by WordPress&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;!--end #copy_power--&gt;\r\n\r\n</pre>\n<p>Nh vy l chng ta  dng xong code HTML cho giao din ca mnh. Vic cn li l mnh s validate code &#8220;Ht T M L&#8221;, phn ny cc bn hy t lm, mnh  validate code ri.</p>\n<h5>FINALLY: REVIEW RESULT</h5>\n<p>Kt hp cc phn code trn, <a href="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/tommy/tutorial/demo%20post%201%20%28html%29/index.html" title="index" target="_blank">giao din HTML hon chnh</a> ca chng ta  hon thnh.</p>\n<p>Tha thng xng ln, chng ta chi lun phn CSS.</p>\n<h5>Bc 1 : RESET CSS</h5>\n<p>u tin ta phi cho tt c cc th c gi tr mc nh tr v 0 ht. Font-size l 100%, vertical-align l baseline (ci ny chc cng ko cn v mc nh  l baseline ri), background l transparent.</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\nhtml,body,div,span,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6,\r\np,a,font,img,b,u,i,ol,ul,li,fieldset,form {\r\nmargin: 0;\r\npadding: 0;\r\nborder: 0;\r\noutline: 0;\r\nfont-size: 100%;\r\nvertical-align: baseline;\r\nbackground: transparent;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Tip theo mnh s i reset ci th body. Mnh cho font-size l 62.5%, ci ny nu bn  xem ht cc tut khc v psd sang html ri th chc  bit, nhng mnh xin ni li ln na.<br />\nKhi cho 62.5% th v d nh nu l 1em th bng 10px, 1.4em = 14px (gi tr px gp 10 gi tr em). Ni chung ci ny lm cho vic i n v t px sang em hay cc n v khc th d hn thi. Font-family th font chnh ca mnh l tahoma, tip n l arial, cui cng lun phi l sans-serif v sans v serif l h ca tt c cc font khc (hi kh hiu, nm na l th !!). Line-height l 2em nhm lm cho khong cch gia cc dng gin ra t cho d c. Chng ta vit tip :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\nbody {\r\nfont-size: 62.5%;\r\nfont-family: tahoma, arial, sans-serif;\r\nline-height: 2em;\r\nbackground: #0e0e0e url(images/body_bg.jpg) no-repeat left top;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Mnh cho mu ca background v cc bn th b ci mu i th background ca c ci mn hnh phn trn l cc hnh body_bg.jpg cn phn di trng bc, do  cho mu nn l #0e0e0e (trng vi ci mu phn di ca hnh body).</p>\n<p>Ngoi ra chng ta cn cn nh dng thm mt vi ci c bn khc na :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\nol,ul {list-style: none;} /*B i my ci list style ca ol v ul*/\r\n\r\na {\r\ntext-decoration: none; /*B hiu ng gch chn*/\r\n}\r\n\r\na img {\r\nborder: none; /*B border img nu dng nh lm link*/\r\n}\r\n\r\nimg {\r\nvertical-align: center;\r\n}\r\n\r\n:focus {\r\noutline:0;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Bn c nh  phn trc, mnh c cho mt s tag c class l uppercase v bold ko ? Mc ch l  nh dng nh sau :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n.uppercase {\r\ntext-transform: uppercase;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.bold {\r\nfont-weight: bold;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Cui cng l div#wrapper bao quanh ton b ni dung trang web. Mnh  o trong photoshop width v margin ca n :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#wrapper {\r\nwidth: 960px;\r\nmargin: 37px auto;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Sau bc reset ny, chng ta c kt qu nh <a href="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/tommy/tutorial/demo%20post%202%20%28css%29/reset/" title="reset_css" target="_blank">demo</a>.</p>\n<h5>BC 2 : TOP_PAGES</h5>\n<p>By gi chng ta bc sang style div#top_page :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#top_page {\r\nbackground: white;\r\nposition: relative;\r\noverflow: hidden;\r\nborder-radius: 5px 5px 0px 0px;\r\nbehaviour: url(border-radius.htc);\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p> y mnh cho position l relative v lt na mnh s apply absolute positioning cho cc children element ca n. V ci logo mnh cho float left nn phi t overflow l hidden.<br />\nCc bn nhn k trong psd th n c radius  pha trn nn t border-radius. Ngoi ra xin gii thiu vi cc bn cch hack ci border radius ny trong IE,  chnh l file border-radius.htc (file ny mnh  trong source code, cc bn c th down v). Cc bn ch cn thm lnh behaviour: url(border-radius.htc) l IE s hin th c ci border-radius.</p>\n<p>Tip theo l n ci logo,  trn mnh  ni l cho float left, ngoi ra cn chnh margin cho n na ch :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#top_page img {\r\nmargin: 36px 0px 25px 41px;\r\nfloat: left;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>K n l p#telephone, mnh s p dng absolute cho tag ny, n nm  gc trn bn phi nn ta t top v right l 0. Mnh t file phone_bg.png lm background, size file ny l 221 x 31 px nn t width l 221px, height l 31px. Cui cng l t background, v l nh dng png nn mu nn l transparent :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#top_page p#telephone {\r\nposition: absolute; top: 0px; right: 0px;\r\nwidth: 221px; height: 31px;\r\nbackground: transparent url(images/phone_bg.png) no-repeat top left;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>n ci th a nm trong p#telephone, u tin mnh bin n thnh block. Sau  chnh margin cho n ra chnh gia. t background l ci hnh phone,  trnh s v hnh  ln nhau th thm text-indent. Ngoi ra cn cn chnh size v color khi khng di chut v khi di chut ln n na nh :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#top_page p#telephone a {\r\ndisplay: block;\r\nfont-size: 18px; color: #c9c9c9; text-indent: 30px;\r\nmargin: 6px 0px 6px 54px;\r\nbackground: transparent url(images/phone.png) no-repeat top left;\r\n} \r\n\r\n#top_page p#telephone a:hover {\r\ncolor: #585858;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>n ci ul#pages, mnh p dng position cho n :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#top_page ul#pages {\r\nposition: absolute;\r\nbottom: 21px; right: 31px;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>n li bn trong ul#pages mnh cho n thnh inline  n thnh hng ngang :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#top_page ul#pages li {\r\ndisplay: inline;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Tip theo l a bn trong li, mnh cn t height cho tag a l 24px v lt na khi to hiu ng hover mnh s t background cho a l pages_bg.jpg (file ny c height l 24px). Mun th th mnh phi bin a thnh block element, nhng lm th th ul ca mnh li nm dc mt, cho nn mnh phi cho float left. nh dng thm font-family, size, color, mt cht margin, padding v border radius na. Chng ta vit tip :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#top_page ul#pages li a {\r\nfont-family: &quot;arial&quot;, tahoma, sans-serif;\r\nfont-size: 12px; color: #808080;\r\ndisplay: block; height: 24px; float: left;\r\nline-height: 24px; margin-right: 37px;\r\npadding: 0px 15px; \r\nborder-radius: 5px; behaviour: url(border-radius.htc);\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>By gi mnh to hiu ng hover nh ti ni  trn. Tuy nhin ci tag a u tin ti mun n lun c background, nn mnh thm b chn li:first-child na :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#top_page ul#pages li a:hover, #top_page ul#pages li:first-child a {\r\nbackground: url(images/pages_bg.jpg) repeat-x top left;\r\ncolor: white;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>OK, n bc ny mnh  lm xong phn top page. Mnh c nh <a href="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/tommy/tutorial/demo%20post%202%20%28css%29/top_page/" title="top_page_css" target="_blank">demo</a>.</p>\n<h5>BC 3: HEADER</h5>\n<p>Mnh cho header c width l 100%, mt thnh phn c cho width 100% th s c width bng vi thnh phn parent element ca n.  bc reset CSS mnh cho div#wrapper width l 960px, do  div#header s c width 960px. Tht ra bn cng c th t trc tip 960px lun cho div#header, nhng khi t 100% th nu mnh thay i width ca div#wrapper th width ca div#header cng thay i theo m khi phi t li na :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#header {\r\nwidth: 100%;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<h5>a) BANNER</h5>\n<p>Mnh s t file header_bg.jpg (size 960 x 335px) lm background, do   mnh t width 960px v height 335px. Cui cng l position relative  apply absolute cho cc element trong n :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#header #banner {\r\nwidth: 960px; height: 335px;\r\nbackground: url(images/header_bg.jpg) no-repeat top left;\r\nposition: relative;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>i vi p#success, mnh p dng absolute positioning, sau  t size, font-family, color, width v line-height :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#header #banner p#success {\r\nposition: absolute; top: 84px; left: 51px;\r\nfont-size: 29px;\r\nfont-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, tahoma, sans-serif;\r\ncolor: white; width: 370px; line-height: 1.3em;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>n p#started, mnh cng dng absolute, mnh t background l file started.jpg (size 254 x 51px) nn cn t width v height tng ng l 254px v 51px, t thm line-height cho khong cch gia cc dng cch ra mt cht. Thm indent cho n ra gia cht v cui cng l border radius. Code ca chng ta :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#header #banner p#started {\r\nposition: absolute; top: 221px; left: 55px;\r\nwidth: 254px; height: 51px; line-height: 51px;\r\nbackground: url(images/started.jpg) repeat-x top left;\r\ntext-indent: 26px; \r\nborder-radius: 5px; behaviour: url(border-radius.htc);\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Mc ch mnh thm span vo p#started trong HTML l  t background l ci hnh mi tn (bn view file psd y). Mnh s bin n thnh block  chnh margin l auto cho n, cho n cn ra tri bng text-align l left. Cui cng l t background, bn lu  vi phn background-position mnh cho 219px 50%, 219px tc l cho ci hnh cch l tri 219px, cn 50% l  n cn gia theo chiu dc :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#header #banner p#started span {\r\nmargin: auto; display: block; text-align: left;\r\nfont-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, tahoma, sans-serif;\r\ncolor: #b90016; font-size: 20px;  \r\nbackground: transparent url(images/started.png) no-repeat 219px 50%; \r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>n ci img trong div#banner, mnh s p dng absolute cho n. Mnh cho bottom l gi tr m, thay v y ln trn th n s b y xung di, vt ra ngoi ci div#banner mnh  design ban u trong photoshop :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#header #banner img {\r\nposition: absolute; bottom: -28px; right: 30px; \r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<h5>b) FEATURED POST</h5>\n<p>u tin, ta style width v mu nn ca div#featured_post :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#header #featured_post {\r\nwidth: 100%;\r\nbackground: #ededed;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>n ci ul, u tin mnh thm padding, nhng nu c padding th  ln ca ul s b thay i, y l l do mnh phi dng div#featured_post bao quanh ci ul (mc d ul  l block element), khi thm padding cho ul th  ln ca div#featured_post s ko b nh hng (nu bn vn cha hiu ci ny, xem li bi Box Model). V mnh cho cc li trong ul float nn phi cho overflow l hidden :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#header #featured_post ul {\r\npadding: 38px 0px 22px 53px;\r\noverflow: hidden; \r\n} \r\n</pre>\n<p>n li trong ul, mnh cho float left, width l 245px, margin-right  cc list cch ra cho d nhn :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#header #featured_post ul li {\r\nfloat: left; width: 245px;\r\nmargin-right: 40px;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Trong tng li, mnh nh dng nh sau :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#header #featured_post ul li img {\r\nfloat: left; margin-right: 18px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#header #featured_post ul li p {\r\nfont-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;arial&quot;, tahoma, sans-serif;\r\ncolor: #4f4f4f;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#header #featured_post ul li p span {\r\ndisplay: block; font-size: 15px;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Bn xem <a href="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/tommy/tutorial/demo%20post%202%20%28css%29/header/" title="header_css" target="_blank">demo</a>  thy kt qu sau bc ny.</p>\n<h5>BC 4 : CONTENT</h5>\n<p>Vi phn div#content, mnh t background l white v thm padding. Lu  l mnh phi cho overflow hidden v mnh s cho cc div.post_item bn trong n float :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#content {\r\nbackground: white;\r\npadding: 41px 20px 52px 20px;\r\noverflow: hidden;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>n cc div.post_item, nh mnh va ni  trn l s cho float left, t margin left  cch cc div ra. Nhng cc bn thy mi div li trn 1 hng, do  t width 265px (mnh o trong photoshop)  cc div c ngang hng vi nhau. Cui cng l t font-family :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#content .post_item {\r\nfloat: left; margin-left: 33px;\r\nwidth: 265px; \r\nfont-family: &quot;arial&quot;, tahoma, sans-serif;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Vi ci phn tiu  h1, n gin ch cn chnh size v hiu ng hover tag a trong n :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#content .post_item h1 a {\r\nfont-size: 25px;\r\ncolor: #585858;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#content .post_item h1 a:hover {\r\ncolor: #0f4db6;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>n ci img ca mi post, mnh t margin top v bottom  n cch ra vi ci tag h1 v on paragraph  di :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#content .post_item img {\r\nmargin: 24px 0px 20px 0px;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Vi ci tag p  di, mnh cng ch cn chnh size v color :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#content .post_item p {\r\nfont-size: 12px;\r\ncolor: #4f4f4f;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>n ci a class read_more ny hi phc tp mt cht. u tin mnh chnh margin top  n cch ra vi ci tag p  trn. Vi tag a ny mnh cn t background, do  cn phi t width v height cho n. Vy mnh cn phi cho n display l block (tag a mc nh l inline), sau  t width 96px v height 27px (bng vi kch thc ca hnh lm background 96 x 27px). t text-align center  text cn ra gia theo chiu ngang, t line-height bng vi height, tc 27px  text cn ra gia theo chiu dc (khi bn cho line-height bng vi height ca mt thnh phn th text ca n s cn ra gia theo chiu dc). Thm style font-family, size v color cho n ging vi design trong file PSD. t background l file readmore_bg.jpg, mnh mun n lp li theo chiu ngang nn cho repeat-x. Cui cng l thm border v radius. Bn lu  mnh ch cn border left v right thi, cn border top v bottom th trong hnh background  c ri, do  mnh cho border top v bottom l none. Tm li code ca mnh :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#content .post_item a.read_more {\r\nmargin-top: 20px;\r\ndisplay: block; \r\nwidth: 96px; text-align: center;\r\nheight: 27px; line-height: 27px;\r\nfont-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;tahoma&quot;, sans-serif;\r\ncolor: #6c6c6c;\r\nbackground: url(images/readmore_bg.jpg) repeat-x top left;\r\nborder: 1px solid #ccc; \r\nborder-radius: 5px; behaviour: url(border-radius.htc);\r\nborder-top: none; border-bottom: none;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Chuyn sang tag ul c trong div post_item th 2, mnh chnh margin top, cn ci list-style  bn trong nn cho l inside, mnh s ly file list_style.png lm list-style-image :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#content .post_item ul {\r\nmargin-top: 20px;\r\nlist-style: inside url(images/list_style.png);\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>n tng ci li trong ul, mnh nh dng padding v border bottom  tch cc li ra cho d nhn hn :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#content .post_item ul li {\r\npadding: 5px 0px 5px 0px;\r\nborder-bottom: 1px dotted #d3d3d3;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Ring ci li cui cng mnh ko cn border bottom, do  mnh dng b chn last-child :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#content .post_item ul li:last-child {\r\nborder-bottom: none;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Cui cng l tag a trong li, n gin cng ch style ci size, font-family v hiu ng hover cho n thi :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#content .post_item ul li a {\r\nfont-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;arial&quot;, tahoma, sans-serif;\r\ncolor: #0f4db6;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#content .post_item ul li a:hover {\r\ncolor: #585858;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Giao din ca phn content nh <a href="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/tommy/tutorial/demo%20post%202%20%28css%29/content/" title="content_css" target="_blank">demo</a>.</p>\n<h5>BC 5 : FOOTER</h5>\n<p>Vi div#footer ny, u tin mnh cho background l mu trng, thm border-top nh trong psd, sau  thm radius v padding :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#footer {\r\nbackground: #ededed;\r\nborder-top: 2px solid #bababa;\r\nborder-radius: 0px 0px 5px 5px; behaviour: url(border-radius.htc);\r\npadding: 24px 41px;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>n ci ul vi id info_footer, mnh cho border bottom v padding bottom  cch ra mt cht vi ci ul  di, sau  cho n overflow l hidden v mnh s float cc li trong n :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#footer ul#info_footer {\r\noverflow: hidden;\r\nborder-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;\r\npadding-bottom: 12px;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Tip theo l tag li con ca ul#info_footer, mnh cho float left, t margin left  cch cc li ra, nh dng cho text l font-family, size v color. Bn xem trong file psd th thy cc li ngang hng vi nhau, nh vy mnh s nh dng thm width. Bn ch  mnh ang ni n nhng tag li l con ca ul#info_footer thi, do  phn style ny mnh dng b chn &gt; :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#footer ul#info_footer &gt; li {\r\nwidth: 300px; \r\nfloat: left; margin-left: 100px;\r\nfont-size: 12px; color: #4f4f4f;\r\nfont-family: &quot;arial&quot;, tahoma, sans-serif;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Tuy nhin bn thy ci li cui cng vn b chui xung di, do  mnh dng b chn first-child v last-child  nh dng li width v margin left cho ci li u tin v cui cng sao cho thch hp :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#footer ul#info_footer &gt; li:first-child {\r\nwidth: 107px;\r\nmargin-left: 0px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#footer ul#info_footer &gt; li:last-child {\r\nmargin-left: 65px;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>n tag h3 trong mi li, ch yu style text v size, color v margin :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#footer ul#info_footer li h3 {\r\nfont-size: 15px;\r\ncolor: #585858;\r\nmargin-bottom: 28px;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>n tng tag a trong mi li, cng n gin l hiu ng hover thi :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#footer ul#info_footer li ul li a {\r\ncolor: #4f4f4f;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#footer ul#info_footer li ul li a:hover {\r\ncolor: #0f4db6;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Bn thy khi vit code HTML th trong li cui ca ul#info_footer mnh c cho mt s tag p, style margin cho n :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#footer ul#info_footer &gt; li:last-child p {\r\nmargin-bottom: 17px;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>n cc span cng nm trong li cui, mnh mun n nm ring trn mt hng, nhng n li l inline element m, rt n gin :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#footer ul#info_footer li span {\r\ndisplay: block;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>Chuyn sang phn cui cng, ul#copy_power, u tin, nh my tag  trn, mnh cng style tng t (mnh cng cho overflow l hidden v s float cc li):</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#footer ul#copy_power {\r\nborder-top: 1px solid white;\r\noverflow: hidden;\r\npadding-top: 21px;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p>n li trong ul#copy_power, mnh float left, thm font-family, size, color, vi ci li cui mnh cn background nn cho thm height v line-height bng vi height  cn text ra gia theo chiu dc :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#footer ul#copy_power li {\r\nfloat: left;\r\nfont-family: &quot;arial&quot;, tahoma, sans-serif;\r\nfont-size: 12px;\r\ncolor: #4f4f4f;\r\nheight: 16px; line-height: 16px;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<p> l nh dng chung cho li u tin, cn li th 2 cn style thm mt cht, vi b chn last-child, ta cho n float right, width l 275px, background l hnh icon.png, mnh mun n ch xut hin mt ln nn cho no-repeat, vi background position th cho 0 50%  cn hnh ra gia theo chiu dc, cui cng l text-indent 128px  tch phn text v background khi chng ln nhau :</p>\n<pre class="brush: css; title: ; notranslate">\r\n#footer ul#copy_power li:last-child {\r\nfloat: right;\r\nwidth: 275px;\r\nbackground: transparent url(images/icon.png) no-repeat 0 50%;\r\ntext-indent: 128px;\r\n}\r\n</pre>\n<h5>FINALLY: REVIEW RESULT</h5>\n<p>Well, very good !!! Chng ta  hon thnh phn code CSS v bn hy <a href="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/tommy/tutorial/demo%20post%202%20%28css%29/index/" title="index_css" target="_blank">xem kt qu cui cng</a>.</p>\n<p>y l tut u tin nn mnh vn cn rt nhiu thiu st, rt mong cc bn nhit tnh comment gp   trong tut sau mnh c th lm tt hn. Okay, I hope you like this tutorial. Thank you for your time and talk to you soon. Goodbye !!!</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:62:"http://www.izwebz.com/css/psd-sang-html-bussiness-layout/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2:"72";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:22:"WordPress Post Formats";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:66:"http://www.izwebz.com/wordpress/essentials/wordpress-post-formats/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:75:"http://www.izwebz.com/wordpress/essentials/wordpress-post-formats/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Thu, 01 Aug 2013 07:04:23 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:10:"Essentials";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:29:"http://www.izwebz.com/?p=5270";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:617:"WordPress Post Formats c gii thiu  phin bn WP 3.1, vi post formats bn c th to ra cc bi vit vi cc ni dung, nh dng khc nhau. Bn c th da vo n  c th style cc bi vit vi mu sc, b cc khc nhau. Khai bo Post Formats Mc nh Post Formats s khng c kch hot, tr khi bn s dng cc theme thng mi hoc cc theme mc nh ca WP. Nu bn t vit mt theme wordpress t a-z th bn phi tin hnh khai bo  functions.php  tin hnh [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:14:"V Minh Mn";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6666:"<p>WordPress Post Formats c gii thiu  phin bn WP 3.1, vi post formats bn c th to ra cc bi vit vi cc ni dung, nh dng khc nhau. Bn c th da vo n  c th style cc bi vit vi mu sc, b cc khc nhau.<br />\n<span id="more-5270"></span></p>\n<h5>Khai bo Post Formats</h5>\n<p>Mc nh Post Formats s khng c kch hot, tr khi bn s dng cc theme thng mi hoc cc theme mc nh ca WP. Nu bn t vit mt theme wordpress t a-z th bn phi tin hnh khai bo  functions.php  tin hnh kch hot.</p>\n<pre class="brush: php; title: ; notranslate">\r\nadd_theme_support(''post-formats'', array(''aside'', ''link'', ''gallery'', ''status'', ''quote'', ''image''));\r\n</pre>\n<p>WordPress ch cho developer s dng cc post formats nh trn. Ngoi ra, bn hon ton khng th thm post formats no khc. Nu khng kch hot th cc bi vit c mc nh format l Standard. Nu bn khng cn dng format no th c vic b n ra khi array thi. Trong v d ny thi ch s dng 3 format u tin thi.</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image"><img src="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/mrv2m/wp-format.jpg" alt="Wp post format" /></div>\n<p><em>Nu  kch hot ri m bn vn khng thy Post Formats hin th th bn c th bm vo Screen Option v check chn Format.</em></p>\n<h5>Khai bo get_post_format()</h5>\n<p>Hm get_post_format() thng c s dng pha trong loop. Bi v get_post_format() phi truyn vo id ca bi vit  n tr v kt qu l format ca bi vit m ta ang xem.</p>\n<pre class="brush: php; title: ; notranslate">&lt;?php $format = get_post_format($post-&gt;ID); ?&gt;</pre>\n<p>By gi th cng vic cn li ca chng ta l s dng if&#8230;else  tin hnh ra iu kin cho cc dng format khc nhau, v mi ng format s c cu trc html&#038;css khc nhau  c th hin th theo  mun ca bn thi.</p>\n<pre class="brush: php; title: ; notranslate">\r\n&lt;?php if ( have_posts() ) : while ( have_posts() ) : the_post(); ?&gt;\r\n&lt;!-- post --&gt;\r\n&lt;?php $format = get_post_format($post-&gt;ID); ?&gt;\r\n&lt;?php if ($format == ''aside'') { ?&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;!-- HTML &amp; CSS ca bi vit vi format aside --&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;?php }elseif ($format == ''link'') { ?&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;!-- HTML &amp; CSS ca bi vit vi link --&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;?php }elseif ($format == ''gallery'') { ?&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;!-- HTML &amp; CSS ca bi vit vi gallery --&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;?php }else { ?&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;!-- HTML &amp; CSS ca bi vit vi format mc nh--&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;?php } ?&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;?php endwhile; ?&gt;\r\n&lt;!-- post navigation --&gt;\r\n&lt;?php else: ?&gt;\r\n&lt;!-- no posts found --&gt;\r\n&lt;?php endif; ?&gt;\r\n</pre>\n<h5>ng dng th vi format video</h5>\n<p>By gi chng ta s to mt bi vit mi vi format l video, v chng ta nhng video trc tip vo website thng qua iframe m youtube cung cp.</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image"><img src="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/mrv2m/video-formar.jpg" alt="Video post format" /></div>\n<p>Do iframe hu nh c cu trc nh nhau, ch thay i mi id video ca youtube. Do  chng ta ch cn ly id youtube video v b vo ni dung ca bi vit thi, ri dng get_the_content(); gi ra  s dng.</p>\n<pre class="brush: php; title: ; notranslate">\r\n&lt;?php if ($format == ''video'') { ?&gt;\r\n&lt;h1&gt;&lt;?php the_title(); ?&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;youtube&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;iframe width=&quot;560&quot; height=&quot;315&quot; src=&quot;http://www.youtube.com/embed/&lt;?php echo get_the_content(); ?&gt;&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;?php } ?&gt;\r\n</pre>\n<h5>ng dng has_post_format()</h5>\n<p>Hm ny s hin th ni dung c n nh sn cho rt c cc bi vit c format tng ng.  s dng c th chng ta cn phi truyn vo post format v id ca bi vit.</p>\n<pre class="brush: php; title: ; notranslate">\r\n&lt;?php if (has_post_format(''link'',$post-&gt;ID)) { ?&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;Bi vit ny ti tm thy trn Google, v ti hon ton khng chu bt k trch nhim g v ni dung ca bi vit ny.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;?php } ?&gt;\r\n</pre>\n<p>Trong v d trn, cc bi vit no c format l link, th n s lun hin th ra on ni dung nh trn. y l mt th thut kh hay cho cc bloger thng copy bi vit t cc website khc.</p>\n<h5>Chc nng ca tng format</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Standard</strong>: Mt bi vit thng thng, y l format mc nh nu nh khng c khai bo post-formats cho theme</li>\n<li><strong>Aside</strong>: Mt bi vit, nhng khng cn phi c tiu .</li>\n<li><strong>Gallery</strong>: Th vin nh.</li>\n<li><strong>Link</strong>: Thng c lin kt n mt bi vit  mt website khc.</li>\n<li><strong>Image</strong>: Ch c mt hnh nh duy nht.</li>\n<li><strong>Quote</strong>: Mt cu ni, mt cu chm ngn hoc tc ng.</li>\n<li><strong>Status</strong>: Dng  cp nht mt trng thi, ging nh status ca facebook. </li>\n<li><strong>Video</strong>: bi vit ng ti mt video, c th video t youtube hoc vimeo chng hn.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>WordPress Post Formats trong WP 3.6</h5>\n<p>Tuy rng, post format rt hay v a dng, tuy nhin, nhiu ngi vn cha bit n n v s dng n mt cch thng xuyn hn. Chnh v th, trong phin bn WP 3.6, nh pht trin WP  nng cp UI cho post format, lm cho ngi dng cm thy t m v hng th hn vi post format.</p>\n<div class="tutorial-image">\n<img src="http://www.izwebz.com/wp-content/uploads/mrv2m/post-3.6.png" alt="Wp Post 3.6" />\n</div>\n<h5>Kt lun</h5>\n<p>Post formats rt d s dng. Vi tnh nng ny bn c th lm cho website ca bn tr nn phong ph v r rng hn. Ngoi ra, y cng l mt tnh nng kh hay ca WP  gip cho ngi dng c th qun l cc bi vit ca mnh mt cch hp l.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:71:"http://www.izwebz.com/wordpress/essentials/wordpress-post-formats/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"8";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:45:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"Fonts for Web: Icon fonts";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:51:"http://www.izwebz.com/css/fonts-for-web-icon-fonts/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:60:"http://www.izwebz.com/css/fonts-for-web-icon-fonts/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Sat, 27 Jul 2013 13:59:59 +0000";s